code: @Override public void process(Exchange exchange) throws Exception {     ORU_R01 msg = exchange.getIn().getBody(ORU_R01.class).     // map to Patient     Patient patient = getPatient(msg).     exchange.getIn().setBody(patient). }

/**  * Converts {@link ORU_R01} to {@link Patient}  */ private Patient getPatient(ORU_R01 msg) {     Patient patient = new Patient().     final PID pid = msg.getPATIENT_RESULT().getPATIENT().getPID().     String surname = pid.getPatientName()[0].getFamilyName().getFn1_Surname().getValue().     String name = pid.getPatientName()[0].getGivenName().getValue().     String patientId = msg.getPATIENT_RESULT().getPATIENT().getPID().getPatientID().getCx1_ID().getValue().     patient.addName().addGiven(name).     patient.getNameFirstRep().setFamily(surname).     patient.setId(patientId).     return patient. }
